  <section style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto 80px auto; background: #1e1e1e; padding: 30px; border-radius: 15px; box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);">
    <h2 style="color: #00adb5; border-bottom: 2px solid #393e46; padding-bottom: 10px;">1. SZA - Kill Bill</h2>
    
    <div style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 20px; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 20px;">
      <img src="https://resize-image.vocus.cc/resize?norotation=true&quality=80&url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.vocus.cc%2F9b1a0b31-0290-4206-9287-54d6732c103a.jpg&width=740&sign=NDKb3tU4H4zsCd5RtZ9xZ_NXD2riQpE2EKnQq6yss4s" 
           alt="SZA照片" 
           style="width: 250px; height: 250px; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 10px; border: 3px solid #00adb5;">
      
      <p style="flex: 1; min-width: 300px; font-size: 1.1rem; color: #eeeeee;">
        SZA的熱門歌曲〈Kill Bill〉靈感來自電影《追殺比爾》，歌詞描寫了對前任新戀情的強烈嫉妒與憤怒，表達了「如果我不能擁有你，別人也別想得到」的極端心境。歌曲在SZA的專輯《SOS》中，以輕柔的嗓音唱出充滿報復、心碎和憤怒的情感。
      </p>
    </div>

    <div style="position: relative; padding-bottom: 56.25%; height: 0; overflow: hidden; border-radius: 10px;">
